# Lugarithm — AI integration secrets
# Copy this file to ".env" (same folder) and paste your real key. ".env" is gitignored.
#
# While Unity is open, edits to .env are detected and synced automatically within
# about one second. The manual menu and pre-build sync remain available. This writes
# Assets/Resources/ai_config.json for local prototyping; do not ship a production
# client with a private key embedded in it. Use a backend relay for production.

# Google Gemini API key — powers Co-Pilot hints, Coding Mentor, Heritage Oracle,
# Vibe Coding, and the Living Story engine. Get one at https://aistudio.google.com/apikey
GEMINI_API_KEY=
